metadata.name: Curious Cuore 94
metadata.description:
Oh, Cuore, my beating heart,
You are the rhythm of my life,
The pulse that keeps me moving,
Through joy and pain and strife.

You are the center of my being,
The source of all my passion,
The wellspring of my love,
In you I find my fashion.

With every thump and flutter,
You remind me I'm alive,
You give me strength and courage,
To face the world and strive.

Oh, Cuore, my faithful friend,
You guide me through each day,
You fill me with your warmth and love,
In every beat, you say:

"I am here, I am with you,
Through every step you take,
I'll keep on beating, strong and true,
For you, my heart, I'll never break."

So let me cherish you, Cuore,
And keep you close to me,
For with you, my life is richer,
And my love will always be.
